:::The Destrocons/Falcon/Snare/Tigerhawk/Airazor/Depth Charge:::

::They absorb everything Magmatron says. When he asks if anyone has 
questions, Ramjet speaks up::
Ramjet: I have a question, Lord Magmatron. As you know, me and my team form 
the giant Destructus.  Will we have a place in your new plans?
~~~~~
::Tigerhawk kisses Airazor and she returns the kiss. They lie down under a 
tree... and... well, lets give them a little privacy for now::
~~~~~
::Depth Charge looks around at the chaos all around him. He decides he cant 
take much more of this.  He transforms to beast mode and flys away::

--part1_d.f1cbd46.279a89f3_boundary
